Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2022-04-13 [b5607b074] Fix case sensitivity in psql's tab completion for GUC na
-->

      <listitem>
       <para>
        改进 <application>psql</application> 的 Tab 补全（Shinya Kato，Dagfinn Ilmari Mannsåker，Peter Smith，Koyu Tanigawa，Ken Kato，David Fetter，Haiying Tang，Peter Eisentraut，Álvaro Herrera，Tom Lane，Masahiko Sawada）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e2ce88b58">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;346511313">&sect;</ulink>
